        "description": "<h2><em><strong>Craft and Materials</strong></em></h2><h3><em><strong>The materials and methods behind our wearable art.</strong></em></h3><p> </p><p> </p><p><strong>Recycled Sterling Silver:</strong> Certified sustainable precious metal, chosen to minimize environmental impact without compromising on quality or durability.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Architectural Brass & Copper:</strong> Evolving elements that gain character and a unique patina over time, providing a warm, structural anchor to the warm cobalt tones.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Matte Anodised Aluminium:</strong> Selected for its velvet-touch finish and ethereal weightlessness, and ability to act as a lightweight colour-rich canvas for the artists' original designs.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Brushed Aluminium:</strong> A directional grain that catches light with a soft glow, juxtaposed against the deep pigment of, for example, the Yves Klein cobalt blue.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Sterling Silver Findings:</strong> Hand-finished for seamless, all-day comfort and a hypoallergenic foundation.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Vitreous Enamel:</strong> Hand-applied and kiln-fired to achieve a signature, light-catching lustre that is fused permanently to the copper.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Dual-Finish Disc:</strong> A high-pigment blue enamel face contrasted with a smooth, silver-satin reverse, offering two distinct ways to wear the piece.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Gold-Plated Trace Chain:</strong> A delicate yet durable diamond-cut chain, plated in high-karat gold for a refined, luxurious finish.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Lightweight Engineering:</strong> Carefully balanced proportions to ensure the pendant sits flat against the skin while remaining effortlessly light.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Hand-Finished Assembly:</strong> Every component is inspected and hand-assembled by the artists to ensure quality and precision.</p>",
